               <H2>Market Summary</H2>
               <p>Credit Landing Shopping Centre possesses a strong presence as essentially the only neighbourhood food anchored convenience and service shopping centre serving the affluent Port Credit/Lorne Park/Mississauga Road area of south Mississauga. Credit Landing is conveniently located in Port Credit. The Centre is easily accessible and highly visible from Lakeshore Road West. Credit Landing also has the advantage of superior drawing power as a Loblaws anchored centre. This strong anchor compliments the Centreâ€™s primarily service-based tenant mix. The Loblaws store underwent a complete renovation in 2014.</p>
